好的实现方式推荐吗？</p>\n","last_modified":1621142837,"replies":22,"id":777222},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1618811339","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1618811339","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":172439,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","stars":3226,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"hookybaby","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6e1abf510d756ab24972c03acc7f632b?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hookybaby","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1405144406,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6e1abf510d756ab24972c03acc7f632b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6e1abf510d756ab24972c03acc7f632b?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":67756},"last_reply_by":"mangoDB","last_touched":1621131702,"title":"coinbase 两步验证 app 失效了怎么搞？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777188","created":1621127452,"content":"大概是在 2012 年或 2013 年注册的 coinbase，两步验证一直用的 authy app，最后一次登陆大概是在 2019 年，昨天上去发 authy app 不支持了，登陆时要提供的 6 位，authy 是显示是七位，给客户技术发邮件，自动邮件回复中国地区不提供服务，更要命的是当时注册时名字写的是昵称，所以无法提供 id 证明，帐号，密码，手机号都在，有没有类似经验的老兄，我知道会有人更关心帐户里有多少币，拿回账户后截图公示😅","content_rendered":"<p>大概是在 2012 年或 2013 年注册的 coinbase，两步验证一直用的 authy app，最后一次登陆大概是在 2019 年，昨天上去发 authy app 不支持了，登陆时要提供的 6 位，authy 是显示是七位，给客户技术发邮件，自动邮件回复中国地区不提供服务，更要命的是当时注册时名字写的是昵称，所以无法提供 id 证明，帐号，密码，手机号都在，有没有类似经验的老兄，我知道会有人更关心帐户里有多少币，拿回账户后截图公示😅</p>\n","last_modified":1621127452,"replies":20,"id":777188},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1620107141","name":"android","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1620107141","title":"Android","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","top