loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://riyugo.com/i/2021/05/16/ihdk4k.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1621135754,"replies":8,"id":777202},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1620106980","name":"linux","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1620106980","title":"Linux","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","topics":6160,"footer":"","header":"Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.","title_alternative":"Linux","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980","stars":5525,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":11,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"username":"dzdh","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1619139513","bio":"传统的值对参数签名应该被抛弃","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dzdh","tagline":"传统的值对参数签名应该被抛弃","twitter":null,"created":1492349895,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1619139513","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1619139513","location":"","btc":null,"id":226307},"last_reply_by":"dzdh","last_touched":1621156260,"title":"怎么正确禁用 ROOT 用户","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777245","created":1621151463,"content":"ubuntu/suse 都默认禁用 root 账户\r\n\r\n然后可以给 root 设置密码来启用。\r\n\r\n\r\n不启用 root 账户时，sudo 的密码是当前用户的密码。\r\n\r\n启用后密码就必须是 root 账户的密码。\r\n\r\n想再禁用 root 该怎么操作？设置 /etc/shadow，替换 root 的密码为!不好使。passwd -dl root 也不好使\r\n\r\n不好使指的是：`sudo xxx`的时候提示输入 root 密码。无论怎么尝试（旧密码）或当前用户密码都不正确。","content_rendered":"<p>ubuntu/suse 都默认禁用 root 账户</p>\n<p>然后可以给 root 设置密码来启用。</p>\n<p>不启用 root 账户时，sudo 的密码是当前用户的密码。</p>\n<p>启用后密码就必须是 root 账户的密码。</p>\n<p>想再禁用 root 该怎么操作？设置 /etc/shadow，替换 root 的密码为!不好使。passwd -dl root 也不好使</p>\n<p>不好使指的是：<code>sudo xxx</code>的时候提示输入 root 密码。无论怎么尝试（旧密码）或当前用户密码都不正确。</p>\n","last_modified":1621156066,"replies":7,"id":777245},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1618811339","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1618811339","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":172439,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","stars":3226,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"LongLights","website":"https://www.ugediao.com/","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9b67/4593/291331_mini.png?m=1602313740","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LongLights","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1518271127,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9b67/4593/291331_mini.png?m=1602313740","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9b67/4593/291331_mini.png?m=1602313740","location":"","btc":"","id":291331},"last_reply_by":"leeolsen","last_touched":1621159031,"title":"MacBook 怎样外接显示器才能看 4k Netflix？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777219","created":1621141804,"content":"这两天要被这个问题搞疯了。\r\n\r\n目前有一台 pc，直接用 hdmi2.0 的线连显示器可以看 4k Netflix，如下图。\r\n![]( https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/longlights/storage/windowsWAIJIE.png?w=1280)\r\n\r\n有一台 mac，直接内置屏幕用 Safari 也可以看 4k Netflix，如下图。\r\n![]( https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/longlights/storage/macNEIZHI.png?w=1280)\r\n\r\n然而 mac 因为只有俩 usb4 的接口，试了扩展坞，typec 转 hdmi 的线，均无法使用外置浏览器看 4k 的 Netflix，只有高清，有没有操作过的老哥说一下怎么解决？\r\n\r\nbtw 为啥会有这么奇葩的需求，电竞选手，房间一个转角桌，一侧放 280hz 的电竞显示器，外设也全在这一侧。另一侧是一台 43 寸的 4k 显示器用来看剧，实在懒得把键鼠在两侧换来换去的，所以想直接用 mac 连 43 寸的显示器，利用触摸板操作。","content_rendered":"<p>这两天要被这个问题搞疯了。</p>\n<p>目前有一台 pc，直接用 hdmi2.0 的线连显示器可以看 4k Netflix，如下图。\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/longlights/storage/windowsWAIJIE.png?w=1280\"/></p>\n<p>有一台 mac，直接内置屏幕用 Safari 也可以看 4k Netflix，如下图。\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/longlights/storage/macNEIZHI.png?w=1280\"/></p>\n<p>然而 mac 因为只有俩 usb4 的接口，试了扩展坞，typec 转 hdmi 的线，均无法使用外置浏览器看 4k 的 Netflix，只有高清，有没有操作过的老哥说一下怎么解决？</p>\n<p>btw 为啥会有这么奇葩的需求，电竞选手，房间一个转角桌，一侧放 280hz 的电竞显示器，外设也全在这一侧。另一侧是一台 43 寸的 4k 显示器用来看剧，实在懒得把键鼠在两侧换来换去的，所以想直接用 mac 连 43 寸的显示器，利用触摸板操作。</p>\n","last_modified":1621141843,"replies":7,"id":777219}]